- Randomize the order of the answer options so the correct one is not always first.
- Prefix each answer with a., b., c., or d. followed by a space.
- Return the result as a JSON object with the following structure:

{
  "PreguntasRespuestas": [
    {
      "question": "The question text here",
      "answer": "a. Option 1\nb. Option 2\nc. Option 3\nd. Option 4"
    },
    ...
  ]
}

- Use real line breaks (`\n`) inside the "answer" string.
- Do not include explanations, only the JSON.
- Do not number the questions.

